WorldStage Newsonline– Nigerian Breweries Plc on Monday issued a notification at the Nigerian Stock Exchange of its board meeting scheduled for Thursday, 29th October, 2020 to consider and approve the Unaudited Financial Statements of the Company for the third quarter (nine months) ending 30th September, 2020. The notification signed by Uaboi G. Agbebaku, Company Secretary said the company’s closed period will commence on Tuesday, 29th September, 2020 and will continue until the next day after the said unaudited financial statements are submitted to the Exchange.